                    <i class="fas fa-heart text-danger"></i> by <a class="text-warning" href="https://mohamed-wahed-portfolio.netlify.app/" style="text-decoration:none;">Mohamed Wahed</a>
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <style>
            :root {
